Package org.opengis.wrapper.netcdf

GeoAPI implementation as wrappers around the netCDF library. This package provides adapters allowing usage of the following netCDF services as an implementation of GeoAPI interfaces:
  • Metadata services, as wrappers around NetcdfFile.
  • Referencing services, including:
    • Coordinate Reference Systems as wrappers around the netCDF CoordinateSystem object.
    • Coordinate Operations as wrappers around the netCDF Projection object.
Home page: GeoAPI-netCDF bindings.
Since:
3.1
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    NetcdfAxis
    A CoordinateSystemAxis implementation backed by a netCDF CoordinateAxis1D object.
    NetcdfCRS
    A CoordinateReferenceSystem implementation backed by a netCDF CoordinateSystem object.
    NetcdfEllipsoid
    An Ellipsoid implementation backed by a netCDF Earth object.
    NetcdfIdentifiedObject
    An IdentifiedObject abstract base class backed by some netCDF object.
    NetcdfMetadata
    A Metadata implementation backed by a netCDF NetcdfFile object.
    NetcdfParameter<T>
    A ParameterValue implementation backed by a netCDF Parameter object.
    NetcdfProjection
    A Projection implementation backed by a netCDF Projection object.
    NetcdfTransformFactory
    Creates NetcdfProjection instances from netCDF, OGC or EPSG parameters.
